OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FThe UK has agreed to a US request to
OL,7,Fuse British bases to attack Iranian
OL,8,Fmissile sites, Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FBritain has so far not been involved
OL,12,Fin the US-Israeli strikes on Iran, and
OL,13,Fis reported to have previously refused
OL,14,FAmerican requests to use UK bases for
OL,15,Foperations against the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FBut in a statement on Sunday night,
OL,7,Fthe prime minister said he had granted
OL,8,Fthe request "to prevent Iran firing
OL,9,Fmissiles across the region, killing
OL,10,Finnocent civilians, putting British
OL,11,Flives at risk, and hitting countries
OL,12,Fthat have not been involved".
OL,14,FThe US will use the bases for the
OL,15,F"specific and limited defensive
OL,16,Fpurpose" of hitting missile launch
OL,17,Fsites or storage depots in Iran, he
OL,18,Fadded.
OL,26,@pD@MOUtD@\O]wD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
