PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FStarmer said Britain's allies in the
OL,7,FGulf had "asked us to do more to
OL,8,Fdefend them", and accused Iran of
OL,9,Fputting British lives at risk across
OL,10,Fthe region.
OL,12,FNo British nationals have been harmed
OL,13,Fso far in the conflict, but there are
OL,14,Fat least 200,000 currently in the
OL,15,FGulf, mainly in the UAE, which has
OL,16,Fbeen targeted by multiple Iranian
OL,17,Fmissiles and drones.
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FBritish military personnel were also
OL,7,Fwithin metres of a strike on a base in
OL,8,FBahrain, while regional allies such as
OL,9,FQatar have also come under attack.
OL,11,FAlthough the UK was not involved in
OL,12,Fthe strikes on Iran, it has conducted
OL,13,Fdefensive operations since Saturday
OL,14,Fmorning, including shooting down
OL,15,FIranian drones targeting northern Iraq
OL,16,Fand Qatar.
OL,18,FStarmer said that, despite allowing
OL,19,Fthe US to use British bases, the UK
OL,20,Fwould not be directly involved in
OL,21,Fstrikes against targets in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FIt is not clear which bases the US
OL,7,Fwill use, but US President Donald
OL,8,FTrump has previously referred to using
OL,9,FDiego Garcia, one of the Chagos
OL,10,FIslands in the Indian Ocean.
OL,12,FFollowing the prime minister's
OL,13,Fstatement, the Government published a
OL,14,Fsummary of its legal position, setting
OL,15,Fout that the UK was acting in defence
OL,16,Fof itself and "collective self-defence
OL,17,Fof regional allies who have requested
OL,18,Fsupport".
OL,26,@xD@OOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
