PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FStarmer also issued a joint statement
OL,7,Fwith the leaders of France and Germany
OL,8,Fin which the three men said they would
OL,9,Fwork with the US to enable "necessary
OL,10,Fand proportionate defensive action" to
OL,11,Fdestroy Iranian missiles "at source".
OL,13,FHis statement comes as US and Israeli
OL,14,Fcombat operations against Iran entered
OL,15,Ftheir second day on Sunday.
OL,17,FThe Israeli military said it had
OL,18,Fcontinued to hit sites in central
OL,19,FTehran following the death of Supreme
OL,20,FLeader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei in an
OL,21,Fairstrike on Saturday morning.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@cO]sD@ZOUsD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
