CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FIran has vowed to retaliate with
OL,7,F"devastating blows" and has fired
OL,8,Fmissiles at many of its neighbouring
OL,9,Fcountries as well as US military
OL,10,Ftargets.
OL,12,FThree US service members have been
OL,13,Fkilled and five seriously wounded in
OL,14,Fthe operation so far, according to the
OL,15,FAmerican military's Central Command.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the Foreign Office has
OL,18,Fmounted an unprecedented operation to
OL,19,Fsupport British nationals in the
OL,20,FMiddle East.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
