PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772451406
OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FOfficials at the Foreign Office are
OL,7,Funderstood to be working on plans for
OL,8,Fpotential evacuation routes should
OL,9,Fairspace in the Gulf remain closed.
OL,11,FBut British nationals are currently
OL,12,Fbeing advised to stay where they are
OL,13,Fand follow the instructions of local
OL,14,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,15,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,16,Fofficials expect to change rapidly
OL,18,FThose in Bahrain, Israel, Palestine,
OL,19,FQatar and the UAE have been urged to
OL,20,Fregister their presence with the
OL,21,FForeign Office online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
