OL,3,CUK will allow US to use bases to
OL,4,Cattack missile sites in Iran, PM says
OL,6,FAround 94,000 people have already
OL,7,Fregistered their presence, a scheme
OL,8,Fthe Government has used before to
OL,9,Fprovide urgent updates to people
OL,10,Faffected by international crises.
